        "timestamp": "2017-08-02 01:53:25.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 3:\n\nThe maven settings file has to match the project name\nIn this case, mvn-settings: 'vfc-nfvo-lcm-java-settings' is not valid. \nThis should be vfc-nfvo-lcm-settings. \n\nI think the project name also has to match the actual project name.",
