          "username": "fujinhua"
        },
        "author_role": "OWNER",
        "timestamp": "2017-08-02 03:14:28.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 3:\n\n> The maven settings file has to match the project name\n > In this case, mvn-settings: 'vfc-nfvo-lcm-java-settings' is not\n > valid.\n > This should be vfc-nfvo-lcm-settings.\n > \n > I think the project name also has to match the actual project name.\n\nThis yaml file is inherited from open-o, and the project name is vfc-nfvo-lcm-java, which is diff from vfc-nfvo-lcm-python project, so the mvn-settings also need append java or python.",
        "patchset_number": 3
      },
